Serb President Says FDI ‘Only Cure’ for Jobs, Novosti Reports

-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 
2011-04-07T06:54:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/serb-president-says-fdi-only-cure-for-jobs-novosti-reports.html
Serbia ’s chances of improving
employment depends on it efforts to become a candidate for
European Union membership, which would in turn attract new
foreign investments,  Vecernje Novosti  reported, citing President
 Boris Tadic .  Tadic also said he may consider setting a date for early
elections that opposition parties have demanded if it won’t
jeopardize plans by Serbia to win candidate status by the end of
the year, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
